<br>
Ear slot - Buy the stuff for an Earring of the Solstice, down to under 5k on most servers.<br>
Neck - Clattering Bone Necklace, seems to go for 2kish alot. Also you may want to consider taking a group of folks and killing the nesting/tov valley dragons for one of their Talismans. <br>
Cloak- A Cloak of the Maelstrom would be great for your back also.<br>
Shoulders - if youre on CoV faction, do the Draconic Pauldrons quest, if youre not CoV friendly, look at Barbed Dragonscale Pauldrons, or again consider the Nesting Dragons in the Western Wastes and try to get a Dragonwing Mantle of some sort.<br>
Primary - Frostbringer would be a great wep but would eat up most of your 9k<br>
<br>
You may want to look into some PoG farming for some new bp, legs, bracer, gloves and boots, not to mention some good money making drops.<br>
I also dont see any haste at all, you may want to look into a sash of the dragonborn or or something along those lines.<br>
<br>
Hope that gave ya some ideas. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=528426">Tima</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
